item.title: CVE-2018-12410|2024-08-05T08:38:05.137Z -- tibco%20software%20inc. -- tibco%20spotfire%20statistics%20services
item.description: The web server component of TIBCO Software Inc's Spotfire Statistics Services contains multiple vulnerabilities that may allow the remote execution of code. Without needing to authenticate, an attacker may be able to remotely execute code with the permissions of the system account used to run the web server component. Affected releases are TIBCO Software Inc. TIBCO Spotfire Statistics Services versions up to and including 7.11.0.
